ExecDesc.value: Telestream Flip4Mac WMV Parsing Memory Corruption Vulnerability

EngDesc.value: This threat leverages a flaw in Telestream Flip4Mac's WMV parser via a maliciously crafted wmv file, that when opened will result in memory corruption on the affected system. Telestream Flip4Mac is a client application, this threat delivers the malicious file via a web server listening on port 80.
